<h2 id="aliases">Aliases</h2>

<p>A Bash alias is essentially nothing more than a keyboard shortcut. Eventually with time, a developer tires of typing a specific long command or just want to rename it to something more simple.</p>

<p>Hereâ€™s a small list of the aliases I have in my terminal prompt:</p>

