<p>Then in order to get that information directly in the prompt youâ€™ll just need to invoke that function in the PS1 variable definition:</p>

<p>export  PS1=â€${LIGHT_RED}\u${LIGHT_WHITE} at ${LIGHT_BLUE}\h${LIGHT_WHITE} in ${LIGHT_YELLOW}\w${LIGHT_GREEN}$(git_branch)${NO_COLOR}  \n$ â€œ</p>

